<div class="riskr-about">

  <div class="riskr-about__hero page-width">
    <p class="riskr-about__eyebrow">About Riskr</p>
    <h1 class="riskr-about__headline">
      We don't sell shirts.<br>
      We sell a thesis.
    </h1>
  </div>

  <div class="riskr-about__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-about__body page-width">

    <div class="riskr-about__section riskr-about__section--mission">
      <div class="riskr-about__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-about__label">Our Mission</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-about__content-col">
        <p>Riskr was founded on a single, uncomfortable truth: in modern corporate culture, what you wear communicates your strategic alignment before you open your mouth.</p>
        <p>We engineered a product line that operationalizes this insight. Each garment is a deliverable. Each cotton thread a key result. Wearing Riskr signals to your colleagues, your leadership, and your LinkedIn connections that you are a person who takes human capital seriously.</p>
        <p>This is not a clothing company. This is a human capital optimization platform that happens to sell shirts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-about__divider riskr-about__divider--inner"></div>

    <div class="riskr-about__stats">
      <div class="riskr-about__stat">
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-number">2024</span>
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-label">Year Founded</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-about__stat">
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-number">$0B</span>
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-label">External Funding</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-about__stat">
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-number">12</span>
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-label">Employees Synergized</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-about__stat">
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-number">∞</span>
        <span class="riskr-about__stat-label">Paradigm Shifts Facilitated</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-about__divider riskr-about__divider--inner"></div>

    <div class="riskr-about__section riskr-about__section--competencies">
      <div class="riskr-about__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-about__label">Core Competencies</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-about__content-col">
        <ul class="riskr-about__list">
          <li>Stakeholder Alignment Through Apparel</li>
          <li>Cross-Functional Cotton Procurement</li>
          <li>Brand Equity Cultivation at Scale</li>
          <li>Synergy Materialization &amp; Measurement</li>
          <li>Human Capital Wardrobe Optimization</li>
          <li>Low-Friction Garment Delivery Pipelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-about__divider riskr-about__divider--inner"></div>

    <div class="riskr-about__section riskr-about__section--leadership">
      <div class="riskr-about__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-about__label">Leadership</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-about__content-col">
        <div class="riskr-about__team">
          <div class="riskr-about__team-member">
            <p class="riskr-about__team-name">D. Finney</p>
            <p class="riskr-about__team-role">Chief Executive Officer &amp; Head of Synergy</p>
            <p class="riskr-about__team-bio">A visionary leader with experience operationalizing human capital across multiple verticals. Previously disrupted an industry. Currently disrupting fashion.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-about__team-member">
            <p class="riskr-about__team-name">J. Leverage</p>
            <p class="riskr-about__team-role">Chief Alignment Officer</p>
            <p class="riskr-about__team-bio">Responsible for ensuring all garments are fully aligned with strategic objectives. Holds an MBA and two unsolicited opinions about supply chain optimization.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-about__team-member">
            <p class="riskr-about__team-name">M. Bandwidth</p>
            <p class="riskr-about__team-role">VP, Needle-Moving Initiatives</p>
            <p class="riskr-about__team-bio">Manages all initiatives that move the needle. Has never seen a needle not be moved. Personally accountable for all key results.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="riskr-about__cta-bar">
    <div class="page-width riskr-about__cta-inner">
      <p class="riskr-about__cta-text">Ready to operationalize your wardrobe?</p>
      <a href="{{ routes.collections_url }}/all" class="riskr-about__cta-btn">
        Shop the Collection
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .riskr-about {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .riskr-about__hero {
    padding-block: 100px 80px;
  }

  .riskr-about__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-about__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-about__divider {
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-about__divider--inner {
    margin-block: 0;
  }

  .riskr-about__body {
    padding-block: 0 80px;
  }

  .riskr-about__section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 0 80px;
    padding-block: 72px;
  }

  .riskr-about__label-col {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .riskr-about__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .riskr-about__content-col p {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .riskr-about__content-col p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .riskr-about__stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    padding-block: 64px;
    gap: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-about__stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .riskr-about__stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .riskr-about__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px 40px;
  }

  .riskr-about__list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .riskr-about__list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .riskr-about__team {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .riskr-about__team-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .riskr-about__team-role {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .riskr-about__team-bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-about__cta-bar {
    background: #000;
    padding-block: 64px;
  }

  .riskr-about__cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .riskr-about__cta-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-about__cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    background: #fff;
    color: #000;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    border-radius: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background 0.12s ease, color 0.12s ease;
  }

  .riskr-about__cta-btn:hover {
    background: #d8d8d8;
    border-color: #d8d8d8;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .riskr-about__section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding-block: 56px;
    }

    .riskr-about__stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .riskr-about__team {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 36px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riskr-about__hero {
      padding-block: 72px 56px;
    }

    .riskr-about__stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      padding-block: 48px;
    }

    .riskr-about__list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .riskr-about__cta-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .riskr-about__cta-btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>

